---
title: "Follow a producer (Subscriber)"
---
flowchart TD
    A([Subscriber finds a producer to follow]) --> B[Requests to follow them]
    B --> C{User is a Subscriber?}
    C -- No --> D([Rejected — must have Subscriber role])
    C -- Yes --> E{Target user is a Producer?}
    E -- No --> F([Rejected — target must have Producer role])
    E -- Yes --> G{Already following?}
    G -- Yes --> H([No change — already following])
    G -- No --> I([Now following — their posts will appear in feed])
